## <a id='pas_and_pks'></a>TAS for VMs and TKG-i Installation

A fully meshed TKG-i and TAS for VMs installation based on best practices and reference design considerations will look as follows:

![TKG-i Starter Kit](./images/TA4V_TAS_TKGi_vSphere_NSX-T_MVP3.png)
